OL,6,FChannel 4 hopes to extend its coverage
OL,7,Fof Paralympic sport after seeing off
OL,8,Fthe threat of privatisation.
OL,10,FThe Paralympic movement feared the
OL,11,Fbroadcaster would be forced to drop its
OL,12,Fdecade-long commitment to promoting
OL,13,Fdisabled sport if it were under a
OL,14,Fprofits-driven new owner.
OL,16,FChannel 4 devoted 17 hours a day to
OL,17,Fcoverage from the 2021 Tokyo games, an
OL,18,Fexpensive move which brought few purely
OL,19,Fcommercial benefits.
